Endpoints.Name: Create new user in system
Endpoints.Description:
Create new user in system (admin inly endpoint): 
the following must be provided username, password, password2(same as password), attributes(list of attributes).    
Note: the system may change the username and attributes for compatibility with encrpytion, therefore it is important to look at the response for the finalized values.
The bearer token passed in the authentication header must be one of an admin.

basic authtentication header is "Authorization".
bearer token header is "X-Authorization".
